definition: it is rumored that .../it is reported that ...
according to/to act in accordance with/to depend on/to seize/to occupy

sentences.english: According to the story, the practice of hanging up stockings is connected with St. Nicholas.
sentences.chinese: 据传，悬挂袜子的习俗与圣尼古拉有关。

sentences.english: According to the rumor, Sun Yue will be transfered to the low level league NBDL for the more experiences.
sentences.chinese: 据传孙悦会被下放到低一级别的NBDL去积累经验。

sentences.english: At the same time, the error code in communication is corrected by using of repeat transmittal of data in every cycle.
sentences.chinese: 同时使用数据循环重发，来纠正数据传输中的误码。

sentences.english: According to a legend the mine hides big fortune.
sentences.chinese: 据传说矿山里埋藏着巨大的财富。

sentences.english: A large antenna and several cameras will transmit pictures and data.
sentences.chinese: 一个巨大的天线和几架照相机将进行照片和数据传输。

sentences.english: It was reported that a certain statesman had exercised great political influence over you.
sentences.chinese: 据传某政治家曾对你施加过巨大的政治影响。

sentences.english: "The provider detected enormous amounts of data transfers," Vogt said.
sentences.chinese: “该服务商发现有大量的数据传输，”Vogt表示。

sentences.english: It is traditionally said to have been founded in 18 BC by the legendary leader Onjo.
sentences.chinese: 据传于公元前18年为传奇人物温祚所建。

sentences.english: This is the main passageway through which data travels.
sentences.chinese: 这是数据传输的主要通道。

sentences.english: It is said that his rejection letters reached a height of 5 inches if piled up.
sentences.chinese: 据传说，他收到出版商的退稿信堆起来有五英尺高。

sentences.english: Network system, data transmission device, terminal device and multicasting method.
sentences.chinese: 网络系统，数据传输设备，终端设备和组播方法。

sentences.english: The transmission is partitioned into 2 parts of data handclasp and transmission.
sentences.chinese: 其通讯分为握手和数据传输两阶段。

sentences.english: Legend tells that at the time of his death Swithin was a bishop of Winchester Cathedral.
sentences.chinese: 据传说，斯韦辛死的时候是温切斯特大教堂的主教。

sentences.english: The saw palmetto plant is often said to help hair growth, but there is little clinical evidence concerning its efficacy.
sentences.chinese: 据传塞润榈有生发功效，但是其疗效并没有临床证据。

sentences.english: A more secure data-transfer format wouldn't have been accepted.
sentences.chinese: 因此更安全的数据传输格式未得到广泛的接受。
